      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
        <h2 
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-display font-bold mb-4"
          data-aos="fade-up"
        >
          想加入我們嗎？
        </h2>
        <p 
          class="text-xl text-white/80 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="100"
        >
          如果你對語言教育充滿熱情，想要為孩子們創造更好的學習體驗，歡迎與我們聯繫！
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/contact" 
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary rounded-full font-semibold hover:bg-secondary hover:text-white transition-all hover:scale-105 shadow-lg"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          data-aos-delay="200"
        >
          聯絡我們
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 ml-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    -->
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<!-- AOS Initialization -->
<link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet" />
<script>
  import AOS from 'aos';
  
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    AOS.init({
      duration: 800,
      easing: 'ease-out-cubic',
      once: true,
      offset: 50,
    });
  });
</script>
